<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no, viewport-fit=cover">
    <title>Fast Sokon | مساعد الصيدلي الذكي</title>
    
    <!-- Critical CSS inline -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css" media="print" onload="this.media='all'">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cairo:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" media="print" onload="this.media='all'">
    
    <!-- Firebase SDKs - deferred loading for performance -->
    <script is:inline src="https://www.gstatic.com/firebasejs/9.22.2/firebase-app-compat.js" defer></script>
    <script is:inline src="https://www.gstatic.com/firebasejs/9.22.2/firebase-firestore-compat.js" defer></script>
    <script is:inline src="https://www.gstatic.com/firebasejs/9.22.2/firebase-auth-compat.js" defer></script>
    <script is:inline src="https://www.gstatic.com/firebasejs/9.22.2/firebase-database-compat.js" defer></script>
    <script is:inline src="/firebase-config.js" defer></script>

    <style is:global>
        :root {
            --bg-start: #0a0a1a;
            --bg-end: #12102a;
            --card-bg: rgba(20, 18, 38, 0.85);
            --border-light: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            --border-glow: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
            --purple: #9d8cff;
            --purple-dark: #6b5bdb;
            --purple-glow: rgba(157, 140, 255, 0.2);
            --gold: #ffd966;
            --gold-dark: #e6c450;
            --text-white: #ffffff;
            --text-dim: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
            --text-muted: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
            --danger: #ff6b6b;
            --success: #51cf66;
            --radius-xl: 28px;
            --radius-lg: 20px;
            --radius-md: 16px;
            --radius-sm: 12px;
            --shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            --transition-fast: 0.15s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            --transition-normal: 0.25s ease;
            --font-family: 'Cairo', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
        }

        body {
            font-family: var(--font-family);
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-start), var(--bg-end));
            min-height: 100vh;
            min-height: 100dvh;
            color: var(--text-white);
            padding: 12px;
            position: relative;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
            -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        body::before {
            content: '';
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 30%, var(--purple-glow), transparent 70%);
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 0;
        }

        .app {
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 100%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        /* Header */
        .header {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
            border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
            padding: 14px 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            transform: translateZ(0);
        }

        .logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: baseline;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .logo-icon {
            font-size: 28px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--purple), var(--gold));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .logo-text {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 800;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff, var(--purple));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .profile-btn {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-glow);
            border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
            padding: 8px 16px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition-fast);
            font-family: inherit;
            color: inherit;
            transform: translateZ(0);
            will-change: transform;
        }

        .profile-btn:active {
            transform: scale(0.97);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        .profile-avatar {
            width: 36px;
            height: 36px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--purple), var(--purple-dark));
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
            overflow: hidden;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .profile-avatar img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .profile-name {
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            max-width: 120px;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-overflow: ellipsis;
            white-space: nowrap;
            color: var(--text-dim);
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero-section {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
            border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
            padding: 30px 20px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .hero-icon {
            font-size: 60px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--purple), var(--gold));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .hero-title {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: var(--text-white);
        }

        .hero-subtitle {
            font-size: 15px;
            color: var(--text-dim);
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Camera Card */
        .camera-card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
            border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        }

        .camera-btn {
            width: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(157, 140, 255, 0.15), rgba(255, 217, 102, 0.08));
            border: 1px solid var(--purple);
            color: var(--purple);
            padding: 18px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 12px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition-fast);
            font-family: inherit;
            transform: translateZ(0);
            will-change: transform;
        }

        .camera-btn:active {
            transform: scale(0.98);
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(157, 140, 255, 0.25), rgba(255, 217, 102, 0.15));
        }

        .camera-btn i {
            font-size: 22px;
        }

        /* Features Grid */
        .features-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .feature-card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
            border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
            padding: 20px 16px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: var(--transition-fast);
            transform: translateZ(0);
            will-change: transform;
        }

        .feature-card:active {
            transform: scale(0.98);
        }

        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--purple), var(--gold));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .feature-title {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--text-white);
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .feature-desc {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        /* Status Bar */
        .status-bar {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
            border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
            padding: 12px 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        }

        .sync-status {
            font-size: 12px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
            transition: var(--transition-fast);
        }

        .sync-status.online {
            color: var(--success);
        }

        .sync-status.offline {
            color: var(--danger);
        }

        .sync-status.syncing {
            color: var(--purple);
        }

        /* Footer */
        .app-footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 8px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 11px;
        }

        /* Loading Spinner */
        .loading-spinner {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            border-top-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: spin 0.6s linear infinite;
        }

        @keyframes spin {
            to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }

        /* تحسينات للهواتف الضعيفة */
        @media (max-width: 380px) {
            body {
                padding: 8px;
            }
            
            .hero-icon {
                font-size: 48px;
            }
            
            .hero-title {
                font-size: 20px;
            }
            
            .profile-name {
                display: none;
            }
            
            .features-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }

        @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
            *,
            *::before,
            *::after {
                animation-duration: 0.01ms !important;
                transition-duration: 0.01ms !important;
            }
        }

        .hidden {
            display: none !important;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="app">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo" aria-label="Fast Sokon">
                <i class="fas fa-capsules logo-icon" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                <span class="logo-text">Fast Sokon</span>
            </div>
            <button class="profile-btn" id="profileBtn" aria-label="الملف الشخصي">
                <div class="profile-avatar" id="profileAvatar">👤</div>
                <span class="profile-name" id="profileName">الملف الشخصي</span>
            </button>
        </div>

        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <div class="hero-section">
            <div class="hero-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-robot" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-title">مرحباً بك في Fast Sokon</div>
            <div class="hero-subtitle">مساعدك الذكي لإدارة فواتير الصيدلية بسهولة وأمان</div>
        </div>

        <!-- Camera Section -->
        <div class="camera-card">
            <button class="camera-btn" id="cameraBtn" aria-label="مسح فاتورة جديدة">
                <i class="fas fa-camera-retro" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                مسح فاتورة جديدة
            </button>
        </div>

        <!-- Features Grid -->
        <div class="features-grid">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-bolt" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-title">مسح سريع</div>
                <div class="feature-desc">امسح الفواتير ضوئياً في ثوانٍ</div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-shield-alt" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-title">حفظ آمن</div>
                <div class="feature-desc">بياناتك مشفرة ومحمية دائماً</div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-cloud-upload-alt" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-title">مزامنة سحابية</div>
                <div class="feature-desc">فواتيرك متاحة على جميع أجهزتك</div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-chart-bar" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-title">تقارير ذكية</div>
